    <refsect1 id="xfwm4.xfconf.intro.overview" role="functions_proto">
<!--        <title role="functions_proto.title">Overview</title> -->
        <para>
            Xfwm4 stores its configuration in xfconf channel "xfwm"
        </para>
        <para>
            Xfconf usually (unless configured otherwise) stores channels in XML backend,
            so the file name is:
            <blockquote>
                ~/.config/xfce/xfconf/xfce-perchannel-xml/xfwm4.xml
            </blockquote>
        </para>
    </refsect1>
